Richard Reeves (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Reeves_(actor) 0 Richard Reeves (August 10, 1912 – March 17, 1967), also billed as Dick Reeves, was an American character actor best known for playing henchmen and thugs. He performed in hundreds of film and television roles between the 1940s and 1960s.
